factsheet.heading: History
paragraphs: E H Rabbits (1818-74) was a major contributor to the development of suburban Sutton. This linear walk will look at a number of the buildings he is associated with, starting at his own house and ending with his business premises, while looking at other sites on the way to illustrate the Victorian development of Sutton.
